  "an1.439:1.0": "439–446 ",
  "an1.439:1.1": "Ajjhattaṁ rūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati parittāni suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇāni. ",
  "an1.439:1.2": "Tāni abhibhuyya: ",
  "an1.439:1.3": "‘jānāmi passāmī’ti—",
  "an1.439:1.4": "evaṁsaññī hoti. ",
  "an1.440:1.1": "… ajjhattaṁ rūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati appamāṇāni suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇāni. ",
  "an1.440:1.2": "Tāni abhibhuyya: ",
  "an1.440:1.3": "‘jānāmi passāmī’ti—",
  "an1.440:1.4": "evaṁsaññī hoti. ",
  "an1.441:1.1": "… ajjhattaṁ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati parittāni suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇāni. ",
  "an1.441:1.2": "Tāni abhibhuyya: ",
  "an1.441:1.3": "‘jānāmi passāmī’ti—",
  "an1.441:1.4": "evaṁsaññī hoti. ",
  "an1.442:1.1": "… ajjhattaṁ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati appamāṇāni suvaṇṇadubbaṇṇāni. ",
  "an1.442:1.2": "Tāni abhibhuyya: ",
  "an1.442:1.3": "‘jānāmi passāmī’ti—",
  "an1.442:1.4": "evaṁsaññī hoti. ",
  "an1.443:1.1": "… ajjhattaṁ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati nīlāni nīlavaṇṇāni nīlanidassanāni nīlanibhāsāni. ",
  "an1.443:1.2": "Tāni abhibhuyya: ",
  "an1.443:1.3": "‘jānāmi passāmī’ti—",
  "an1.443:1.4": "evaṁsaññī hoti. ",
  "an1.444:1.1": "… ajjhattaṁ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati pītāni pītavaṇṇāni pītanidassanāni pītanibhāsāni. ",
  "an1.444:1.2": "Tāni abhibhuyya: ",
  "an1.444:1.3": "‘jānāmi passāmī’ti—",
  "an1.444:1.4": "evaṁsaññī hoti. ",
  "an1.445:1.1": "… ajjhattaṁ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati lohitakāni lohitakavaṇṇāni lohitakanidassanāni lohitakanibhāsāni. ",
  "an1.445:1.2": "Tāni abhibhuyya: ",
  "an1.445:1.3": "‘jānāmi passāmī’ti—",
  "an1.445:1.4": "evaṁsaññī hoti. ",
  "an1.446:1.1": "… ajjhattaṁ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati odātāni odātavaṇṇāni odātanidassanāni odātanibhāsāni. ",
  "an1.446:1.2": "Tāni abhibhuyya: ",
  "an1.446:1.3": "‘jānāmi passāmī’ti—",
  "an1.446:1.4": "evaṁsaññī hoti. ",
  "an1.447:1.0": "447–454 ",
  "an1.447:1.1": "Rūpī rūpāni passati … ",
  "an1.448:1.1": "ajjhattaṁ arūpasaññī bahiddhā rūpāni passati … ",
  "an1.449:1.1": "subhanteva adhimutto hoti … ",
  "an1.450:1.1": "sabbaso rūpasaññānaṁ samatikkamā paṭighasaññānaṁ atthaṅgamā nānattasaññānaṁ amanasikārā ananto ākāsoti ākāsānañcāyatanaṁ upasampajja viharati … ",
  "an1.451:1.1": "sabbaso ākāsānañcāyatanaṁ samatikkamma anantaṁ viññāṇanti viññāṇañcāyatanaṁ upasampajja viharati … ",
  "an1.452:1.1": "sabbaso viññāṇañcāyatanaṁ samatikkamma natthi kiñcīti ākiñcaññāyatanaṁ upasampajja viharati … ",
  "an1.453:1.1": "sabbaso ākiñcaññāyatanaṁ samatikkamma nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṁ upasampajja viharati … ",
  "an1.454:1.1": "sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṁ samatikkamma saññāvedayitanirodhaṁ upasampajja viharati …. ",
